通过PHP的mail函数发邮件时报出了错误：501 mail from address must be same as authorization user

查看vi /etc/ssmtp/ssmtp.conf

root=houmian@mavericksmobile.com
mailhub=smtp.exmail.qq.com:465
rewriteDomain=mavericksmobile.com
AuthUser=houmian@mavericksmobile.com   
AuthPass=A123456
FromLineOverride=YES
UseTLS=YES

如果发邮件的from和AuthUser不一致，则会报出该错误。
https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/SSMTP
